<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ shì yī zhǎn dēng 迦南1128</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì yī zhǎn dēng, wǒ yě shì yī zhǎn dēng. tóng zài shén de jiā zhōng fàng guāng míng.
 nǐ shì yī dī shuǐ, wǒ yě shì yī dī shuǐ. huì rù jiāng hé cái néng zī rùn tián yě hé shān lǐng.
 nǐ shì yī lì zhǒng, wǒ yě shì yī lì zhǒng. biàn mǎn tiān yá hǎi jiǎo yǒu jiā bèi de shōu chéng.
 la la la la la, la la la la la, shèng líng yǐ zài zhè de dòng gōng, zài zhè de dòng gōng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1128</hymn_number>
</song>